  "decision_conditions": [
    "Proposed flats 3 and 4 would fall below the minimum dwelling sizes set by Policy D6 of the London Plan (2021) and the Department for Communities and Local Government's Technical Housing Standards - Nationally Described Space Standards (March 2015), and would therefore not provide acceptable living conditions for future occupants contrary to Policy D6 of the London Plan (2021). | The proposed ground floor flat 2 would not provide acceptable living conditions by reason of being a north facing single aspect unit with limited outlook and compromised privacy contrary to section 12 of the National Planning Policy Framework, policy D6 of the London Plan 2021, policies 1.1 (g) (h), 1.2 (h) of the adopted Ealing's Development (Core) Strategy (2012) and policy 7.B of the Ealing Development Management Plan Document (2013)."
